  "text": "Samsung 990 Evo $65 $79 Save $14 The Samsung 990 Evo is a fast and power-efficient SSD, featuring support for both PCIe 4.0 x4 and PCIe 5.0 x2. It promises read speeds up to 5,000MB/s and write speeds up to 4,200MB/s, all while using significantly less power than it larger sibling, the 990 Pro. We've seen Samsung's 990 Evo SSD go on sale before, but this is the best price we've seen in some months, making it the perfect time to pick one up. And while it's a pretty good SSD, we didn't love the initial pricing that Samsung set. Well now, we're seeing a steep discount that drops the 1TB model to just $65. So get it while you can because this deal won't be around for long. 1:11 Related Samsung 990 Evo 2TB review: A bewildering launch for a lackluster SSD Samsung's latest mainstream desktop and laptop M.2 NVMe SSD is a decent enough drive for the right price. What's great about Samsung's 990 Evo SSD? For the most part, you're getting excellent bang for your buck at this price. With the SSD providing reasonable performance, with sequential read speeds that top out at 5,000 MB/s, and sequential write speeds that max out at 4,200 MB/s. It's great for daily use and the perfect upgrade for most desktops and laptops. However, if you're thinking about popping this into a gaming PC, it can be done, but we wouldn't recommend it since it doesn't have DRAM. If playing games is your sole intention, than we recommend going with other M.2 SSD options if your budget allows it. What makes this SSD a little different from others is its compatibility with PCIe 4.0 x4 and PCIe 5.0 x2. And while the Gen5 performance isn't the best, it's an option. But for the most part, we recommend using this as a Gen4 drive. Of course, since this is a Samsung SSD, you're going to get excellent reliability, with the drive rated to handle up to 600 TBW (terabytes written). In addition, Samsung also provides a five-year warranty. Again, what really pushes this SSD over the top is the price. At $65, it's pretty good purchase. So grab it while you can.",
